	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-12 text-center">
			<h1>The Shop</h1>
			<p class="intro">
				Proudly serving MoPar fans since 1978, we have been at our current shop, located in Lynnwood, WA, for nearly 15 years. We work surrounded by memorabilia and old parts that represent the era we love. We are only 15 minutes north of Seattle. Stop by to say hi and roam the aisles...you never know what you'll find!
			</p>
		</div>

		<% images = ["shop-1.jpg", "shop-2.jpg", "shop-3.jpg"] %>
